    This intercepts KeyEvents for a JScrollPane, and determines if they qualify to initiate a page change request for the Controller.

    Decorator class for painting behind a button's main graphic image.

    PrintJobWatcher
    Simple Print Job Watcher.
    SwingController
    Controller is the meat of a PDF viewing application.
    ViewModel
    Data model for the current controller, which maintains state on how a Document is being presented to the user.

    An interface that describes the necessary methods needed for common window management.
